          <strong>How To Play</strong><br />
          <ul class="howtoplay-list">
            <li>
              Regio Vinco is a browser based game where you can test your
              geographic knowledge of various regions from all over the globe
            </li>
            <li>
              To get started, click next to view the various subjects that you
