              <i class="game-mode-icon mdi mdi-brain""></i>
            </div>
            <div class="gametype-info">
              <strong>Training Mode</strong><br />
              For those who need more practice:<br /> Drag the current card on the top right corner of the screen
              to the correct sub-region. The game will no longer highlight the correct region, you must select it yourself
              <br />
              No score will be kept
            </div>
          </div>
        
        <div id="travelmode-card" class="gametype-card postcard">
